]. Can we say that every time a promotion occurs, our prophet algorithm approaches them as holidays?

Yes, they are being calculated as holiday coefficients. There are four different promotion flags. `Promo_low`, `Promo_med`, `Promo_high`, `Promo_holiday`. Basically whenever there is a promotion in the data, based on the discount percentages (i.e. 25% discount) we flag that data point as `promo`. If the promotion is on black friday or christmas (special days), then regardless of discount percentage, it’s flagged as promo_holiday. (*There is an improvement point here to distinguish different discount percentages during special days.*)

